			<h2><a href="http://boardsportsschool.com/2010/03/welcome/" rel="bookmark">Welcome</a>
			<span class="commentcount">(<a href="http://boardsportsschool.com/2010/03/welcome/#respond" title="Comment on Welcome">0</a>)</span></h2>
			<div class="date">March 22, 2010 &bull; Category: <a href="http://boardsportsschool.com/category/lead-story/" title="View all posts in Lead Story" rel="category tag">Lead Story</a>, <a href="http://boardsportsschool.com/category/special-events/" title="View all posts in Special Events" rel="category tag">Special Events</a></div>
			<div class="bigger"><p>Since 2002, the Boardsports team has offered kiteboarding, windsurfing, and stand up paddling instruction, rentals, and retail sales.  With exclusive teaching rights at two of the best beach locations, we assure you the best lesson and gear buying experience in the Bay Area.</p>
